{"tid":1815963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聽聞popo用緊呢支強光電筒叫AcebeamW30係雷射燈","createTime":"2020-01-08T02:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T02:01:17.000Z","uid":327169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d14caa133b4a5f088889441ed781dafc9b7e0ad","tid":1815963,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/965FC7A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F965FC7A.jpg&h=9f3f7cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">絕對係唔可以直射眼睛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一般電筒係用LED係人都知，但係W30係用雷射光束，再經過鏡片嘅折射而產生強光嘅!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N1ZvfV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN1ZvfV7.jpg&h=97111e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D8WtM1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD8WtM1K.png&h=0dadeea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eaBNh8x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeaBNh8x.png&h=8332e9b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iR7ddG1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiR7ddG1.png&h=c85aed83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">W30說明書亦都講明唔可以直射人類或動物眼睛，可以做成傷害</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/khnXFoH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkhnXFoH.png&h=562e628c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">每個人只有一對眼，唔好以為W30只係電筒就唔避開，記住唔好直望呀! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"}]}